<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mn yzrʿ bạlbrkạt</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- man̊ yaz̊raʿu biạl̊barakāt̊
 biạl̊barakāti yaḥ̊ṣudu
 waman̊ bisẖuḥiⁿ̃ yaz̊raʿu
 biạlsẖũḥĩ ạảẙḍaⁿạ yajidu

[V2]
 2- wāl̊muʿ̊ṭī ạảẙḍaⁿạ biạlsũrūr̊
 yuḥibũhu ạlrãbũ ạl̊karīm̊
 ṭūbay̱ limuʿ̊ṭiⁿ bisakẖā
 yugẖ̊nīhi jūduhu ạl̊ʿamīm̊

[V3]
 3- naf̊su ạlsãkẖīĩ tas̊manu
 wāl̊mur̊wī ạảẙḍaⁿạ yar̊tawī
 wālrãbũ min̊ ạảʿ̊lay̱ ạlsãmā
 lạa yan̊say̱ dẖā ạl̊qal̊bi ạlnãqī̃

[V4]
 4- lạa nan̊sa fiʿ̊la ạl̊kẖaẙri
 wāltãẘzīʿa fāl̊waq̊tu qaṣīr̊
 fahadẖihi dẖabāyỉḥu
 bihā masarãẗu ạl̊qadīr̊</lyrics>
</song>